<section class="p-6 bg-gray-50 min-h-screen">

  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">Categories</h1>
  <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">
    The Categories page organizes blogs into structured topics, making it easier for users to explore content based on their interests. Each category groups blogs with similar themes, allowing users to navigate through topics efficiently.
  </p>

  <!-- Purpose & Features -->
  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-12">
    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6">
      <h2 class="font-semibold text-xl text-gray-800 mb-3">Purpose</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 space-y-2">
        <li>Provide structured organization of all blogs.</li>
        <li>Help users find content based on topics they care about.</li>
        <li>Highlight categories with most activity or trending posts.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6">
      <h2 class="font-semibold text-xl text-gray-800 mb-3">What Users Can Do</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 space-y-2">
        <li>Browse categories and subtopics.</li>
        <li>Click on a category to see all related blogs.</li>
        <li>Filter content within a category based on popularity or date.</li>
        <li>Bookmark or follow favorite categories (if logged in).</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Workflow -->
  <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6 mb-12">
    <h2 class="font-semibold text-xl text-gray-800 mb-3">User Workflow</h2>
    <ol class="list-decimal list-inside text-gray-600 space-y-2">
      <li>Open the Categories page.</li>
      <li>Browse the available categories or subtopics.</li>
      <li>Click a category to view all blogs under it.</li>
      <li>Sort or filter blogs based on interest.</li>
      <li>Engage with blogs and follow categories to stay updated.</li>
    </ol>
  </div>

  <!-- Features -->
  <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6">
    <h2 class="font-semibold text-xl text-gray-800 mb-3">Key Features</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 space-y-2">
      <li>Structured organization of content by topics.</li>
      <li>Quick navigation to specific categories.</li>
      <li>Filters for newest or most popular blogs.</li>
      <li>Follow or bookmark categories.</li>
      <li>Responsive layout for desktop and mobile browsing.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

</section>
